snippet.title: Wordeous Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Wordeous

Have you tried saying what you want to say when there are words you can't say? You probably have, but do you want to do it again? Wordeous allows you to play with your friends online. Wordeous is also a fun game that will increase interactivity with viewers for streamers.

Available on Steam

Steam Store: Page:https://store.steampowered.com/app/1441430/Wordeous/
